{
  "_meta": {
    "schema_version": "1.0",
    "purpose": "Layer 3 routing registry. One entry per candidate model. coverage_quality controls whether per-question kNN predictions are trusted (full/medium) or the system falls back to an aggregate prior (low). Models without their required_env_var present are dynamically deactivated at load time; the rest of the registry is unaffected.",
    "last_verified": "2026-05-21",
    "verification_note": "Pricing and model_id values reflect the publicly-published catalogs as of late May 2026 for the providers the project currently has keys for (Groq, OpenRouter, Google AI Studio, Hugging Face, Cohere). Entries for OpenAI and Anthropic are registered but kept dynamically deactivated until those keys are provided. The verify-catalogs script (scripts/verify_provider_catalogs.py, to be added in a later batch) refreshes pricing and adds/removes entries as providers change their lineup.",
    "added_at_baseline": "2026-04-01"
  },

